{"tid":1763823,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[警世] 荷蘭叻: 民調你都信!","createTime":"2019-11-30T15:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T00:15:43.000Z","uid":309695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"01c8054bb51ecc0f0ad748afbb329ed79913073e","tid":1763823,"uid":309695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:46:54.000Z","msg":"首先容我禮貌地屌曬班標題撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n落正題<br />\n我唔會話係民意逆轉<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足唔係condom</span></span><br />\n佢地犧牲爭返黎既支線任務勝利<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以敗曬佢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇返六月至今 <br />\n令市民憤怒既最明顯係警暴<br />\n我地冇嬴過，只係對方自爆失分<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">當我地輕敵</span>，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">班狗唔做野</span>先至係<span style=\"color: red;\">最危險</span>既時候<br />\n民意係浮動既，區選證明香港人有道德之餘仲好有同情心<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得會唔會有左交D斯德哥爾摩症候群發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始同情班狗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我可以答你:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大有人在</span><br />\n<br />\n大家咁辛苦黎到season 2，我都希望見到煲底大團圓<br />\n希望手足可以繼續不割席，不分化，be water，be humble!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日見!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f7b66b38d9b04e981af0e4ca54edcb844f0d40","tid":1763823,"uid":309695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:49:09.000Z","msg":"D 狗好可憐 又要食地溝油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" cl